parameters: Kru: "Well... But what should I do..."

Kru: (First... I need to do something about the villagers being held
hostage. They could use them as shields at any moment...)
Kru: (Hm? What was that memory just now...)

Kru: (The memory of me being killed by Iburu... If it's noisy outside, does
that mean Iburu has started a rebellion...)

Kru: (I should listen to what's happening... But how can I sneak into the
village...)
Kru: (With this, I can get into the village...)
Kru "Mia, where are the ruins located?"
Lutetia "The ruins are in the Sacred Child's Forest."
Lutetia "I am Mia. I've been living with you all this time."

Lutetia "I may have been dressed as a cat, but in truth, I am a goddess
named Lutetia."

Umi "...Yeah. I feel like I've seen it in my dreams many times. We fought
together, you comforted me. So, it's strangely easy to accept."

Lutetia "I see... how mysterious... Well, I brought some clothes. You'll
catch a cold in that outfit, so let's change."
Umi "Somehow... this feels even more embarrassing."

Kru "No... that look... I really feel like it's been a long time since I've
seen it..."

Lutetia "Kru is from five years in the future, so it's natural for him to
feel that way."
Umi "Kru... you came from five years in the future? What does that mean?"

Kru "Yeah... It's a long story... or rather, I don't fully understand it
myself... Anyway, I came back from the future to defeat Shif and Xecilay."

Umi "Ugh... that's an incredible story... But since Mia is here, it must be
true.... Was Umi doing well five years in the future?"

Kru "...No, in the future I came from, Umi was dead. She became a sacrifice
to defeat Xecilay..."
Lutetia "This time it won't happen... We will definitely defeat them..."
Lutetia "Then let's go! First, we head to the Sacred Child's Forest."
"Head to the Temple of Lutecia. It's to the south of the forest..."
